    "description": "Comprehensive Postman collection for ClipSphere backend APIs.\n\nHow to use:\n1) Set collection variable baseUrl (default http://localhost:5000)\n2) Run Auth > Register, then set verificationCode from email\n3) Run Auth > Verify Email (or Login) to auto-store token\n4) Use protected endpoints with Bearer token\n\nUseful variables:\n- token\n- targetUserId\n- targetVideoId\n- targetNotificationId"
  },
